snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 21 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 8th March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma

Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises

snippet.title: Best International Women's Day | Dreamz Unlimited
snippet.description:
International Women's Day (IWD) is a global day celebrating the social, economic, cultural and political achievements of women. The day also marks a call to action for accelerating gender parity.
Marked annually on March 8th, IWD is one of the most important days of the year to, celebrate women's achievements, educate and awareness raise for women's equality, call for positive change advancing women.

snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook Chinese favorite chicken noodles recipe. We can eat this noodles recipe in the street food areas. 

First, we prepare chicken and eggs separately, and then we cook all the items together with the boiled noodles and veggies.

The taste is most delicious and yummy!

snippet.title: Gokuldham ‡§µ‡§æ‡§≤‡•á ‡§ñ‡•á‡§≤‡§®‡•á ‡§≤‡§ó‡•á Ketchup ‡§î‡§∞ Besan ‡§∏‡•á Holi! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Holi Special
snippet.description:
Popatlal tries to make fried snacks for the breakfast but he notices that he does not have any tomato sauce in the house to have with the snacks. So, he tries to call Abdul, but Abdul does not pick his phone up. Popatlal then comes out on the balcony of his house and shouts Abdul‚Äôs name. Bhide and others notice Popatlal shouting so they ask him the reason for his yelling. Popatlal tells everyone that he has made some fried snacks and he needs some tomato sauce to eat with them. Bhide tells Popatlal that he will give him the tomato sauce. Later, Bhide goes to Popatlal with a bottle of tomato sauce and leaves. When Popatlal notices that the tomato is expired he comes downstairs screaming Bhide‚Äôs name. What will Popatlal do now? Let‚Äôs find out.

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Produced By ‚Äì Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #SonyPAL #holi #holispecial #happyholi 

Subscribe to Sony Pal: http:/a/www.youtube.com/sonypalindia

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.title: Peshawar Zalmi vs Quetta Gladiators | Highlights | Pakistan Super League | 8th March 2023
snippet.description:
Peshawar Zalmi batted superbly and posted a mammoth total of 240 runs at the end of their innings. Captain Babar Azam was the star with a century to his name. Peshawar Zalmi looked like the winners even before Quetta Gladiators came to bat, however, Jason Roy had other plans. The opener looked unstoppable as he was dealing in boundaries and went on to make 145 runs from just 63 deliveries. This power-packed knock helped the Quetta Gladiators to win by 8 wickets and 10 balls remaining.

Tere Bin Episode 22 Teaser - 8th March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.title: Mahindra Vs @ArunPanwarx | Scorpio N Sunroof Leak | My Opinions | Gagan Choudhary
snippet.description:
Namaste, This is a very different video on my channel where I will talk about the viral video of Scorpio N by Arun Panwar in which his car's Sunroof leaks water when he puts it under a waterfall. Mahindra responds back with a video where they put another Scorpio N under the same water body.
watch it till the end to understand the entire episode.

01:43 Who is Mahindra & Mahindra?
02:16 Who are users of Cars in India?

03:00 Chain of Incidents.
03:12 What Happened with Arun Panwar?
06:30 Mahindra Replied to Viral Video
07:17 Why Did Sunroof leak on Arun's Scorpion N?

11:49 Sunroof Beading on Scorpion N and Drain Hole
13:20 Conclusion

snippet.title: Ittar - Jasmine Sandlas | BPraak | Jaani | Arvindr Khaira | Desi Melodies
snippet.description:
Desi Melodies is here with the hottest track of the season at the onset of summer, Ittar. Performed by Jasmine Sandlas, the vocal delivery is chilling with Jaani's lyrics that show off the love for her partner over BPraak‚Äôs modern-folk composition complemented by the man behind the lens, Arinvdr Khaira. 

This Punjabi banger is all about the Gulabi Queen‚Äôs mesmerizing voice taking the centerstage to talk about how she wants to adorn herself with the fragrance of ‚ÄòIttar‚Äô (a traditional Indian perfume) and spread it in every inch of her body so that her love can feel her presence even when she's not there. 

Full of metaphors that highlight the depth of romance, Sandlas touches upon the idea of fate and how they‚Äôre destined to be together. The combination of Jaani's layered writing, BPraak's exquisite music, and Arvindr Khaira‚Äôs inimitable visual storytelling; this musical bouquet is exactly how Jasmine concludes - ‚ÄúIf Ittar had a sound, this would be it."

Listen to ‚ÄòIttar‚Äô on your favourite streaming platform - https://bit.ly/Jasmine_Sandlas_Ittar

snippet.description:

Qalandar Episode 42 - [Eng Sub] - Muneeb Butt - Komal Meer - Ali Abbas - Hiba Aziz - 4th March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Qalandar is a story of a girl‚Äôs firm belief in her God and His decisions while the rest of the world continues to hurt, defame and challenge her.

Dur-e-Adan is a young and innocent girl who has grown up under the care of her uncle and aunt. Despite being an orphan at an early age, Dur-e-Adan doesn‚Äôt complain about her challenges and difficulties.

On the contrary, Tabriz is a handsome young man who aspires to achieve great things in life. Living in the same locality, Tabriz‚Äôs parents find Dur-e-Adan suitable for him as a life partner. However, Tabriz‚Äôs life takes a surprising turn when Sumbul hailing from a wealthy family falls in love with him. In efforts to secure his future financially, Tabriz forgets the gift that he has been bestowed in the form of Dur-e-Adan for this world and hereafter. Soon, Tabriz‚Äôs half-heartedness and conflicting loyalties in the form of greed begins to reflect in his relationship with Dur-e-Adan.

Amidst all the atrocities faced by Dur-e-Adan will she continue to be patient with those around her? Will Tabriz realize the respect and love that Dur-e-Adan deserves or will he continue to hurt her? Will Tabriz be able to mend his relationship with Dur-e-Adan?

snippet.title: Nikah Episode 45 - [Eng Sub] - Haroon Shahid - Zainab Shabbir - 5th March 2023  - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Nikah Episode 45 - [Eng Sub] - Haroon Shahid - Zainab Shabbir - 5th March 2023  - HAR PAL GEO

Nikah is a powerful and inspiring story of a young girl‚Äôs fight for her social and religious rights. 
Opinionated and confident by nature, Anusha is a beautiful young girl who knows how to stand up for her rights. After losing her mother at a young age, Anusha has been brought up by her aunt, Umaima with a lot of love and care. Umamia is a bit hesitant about Anusha‚Äôs assertiveness and often makes her understand. 
Class fellows and best friends, Anusha and Haris are in love with each other and soon plan to marry. On the contrary, Hamdaan is a handsome young man who belongs to a wealthy family and is the only son of his father. He falls in love with Anusha on his very first meeting with her however is respectful of Anusha‚Äôs choices.
Anusha‚Äôs hope and dreams come crashing down when Haris challenges her thoughts. The supposedly liberal fabric of Haris and his family is exposed when Anusha takes a stand for her rights. After losing everything, will Anusha stay true to herself and fight against all odds? Despite everything, will Anusha realize her true admirer and supporter in form of Hamdaan?

Writer: Nuzhat Saman

snippet.title: Nadiya Ke Paar Funny Scene | Best Scene Of Nadiya Ke Paar | Holi Special | Sachin Pilgaonkar
snippet.description:
Checkout this Classic Scene from the Classic Movie "Nadiya Ke Paar" released in the year 1982. Starring Sachin Pilgaonkar, Sadhana Singh, Inder Thakur, Savita Bajaj, Sheela David. Watch such classic scene only on @Rajshri 

#nadiyakepaar #bollywoodmovies #romanticmovie 

Synopsis-
The story is based on the first half of a Hindi novel, Kohbar Ki Shart by Keshav Prasad Mishra. A Brahman farmer from Eastern Uttar Pradesh lives with his two nephews. He falls ill and is treated by a Vaidya (indigenous medical practitioner) from another village. When the farmer feels okay, he asks the Vaidya about his fees. The Vaidya asks for the farmer's eldest nephew to marry his eldest daughter. The farmer readily agrees.

Omkar marries the Vaidya's elder daughter Roopa, and they start living happily. Roopa gives birth to a baby. During Roopa's pregnancy, her younger sister Gunja comes to live with her. While there, she falls in love with Omkar's younger brother Chandan.

Learning of their love, Roopa promises to help them marry. But, she dies in an accident; and nobody else knows about the love affair. The farmer and the Vaidya decide that Gunja should marry the widower Omkar, to take care of her sister's baby. But moments before the wedding rituals are completed, Chandan and Gunja's love affair is revealed. He is allowed to marry Gunja with everyone's consent.

The rural culture and languages of Uttar Pradesh are portrayed authentically in the film. The movie is based on the first half of the novel. It changes the partners in the second marriage, as the novel had the proposed marriage between Gunja and Omkar taking place. The novel proceeded with the development of their relationship, where Omkar dies of illness and eventually Gunja also dies leaving Chandan alone.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3713 - 8 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3713: Tapu Sena Ke Holi Plans
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide and other members of the Gokhuldham members are worried about the notorious plans of Tapu Sena on the occasion of Holi. Bhide tells about his dilemma to everyone, and Jethalal assures them that Tapu will not be doing anything naughty. Tapua also assures everyone that they will not disturb anyone during the festival. Iyer discusses his worry as last year he was painted with colours, Babita advises him that they will be testing the colours before applying them. Stay Tuned

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3713, 8 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.description:
#parottarecipeintamil, #layerparottaintamil #parotta

Easy Method of  Parotta making

350gram of Maida flour in the Bowl 
Add required salt ,one spoon oil and mixed well
Adding Boiled water little by little mixed well
make dough chapati consistency.
take idiyappam Achu and filled this batter 3/4
three spoons of cooking oil Grease with plate
make parotta peda shown in the video

cover it Rest in 15mins to 30mins
apply oil in top of peda
then gentle press  make parotta
 cooking parotta in the medium flame
Now your layered parotta is ready..

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises

Lyrics

Mazaa aa jaata hai
Adhoori baaton se
Koi mann jaata hai
Zaroori yaaron se
Jo dekhi na suni aisi
Hume duniya dikhati hai
Deewaane hum nahin hote
Deewaani raat aati hai 
Hume unki uhne meri
Mohabbat yaad aati hai

Nazar aati hain zulfon mein
Ghataein badalon jaisi
Yeh dil karne laga unse
Wafaein paglon jaisi
Usse jab dekhte hain toh
Badal jaata hai yeh lehza
Zubaan pe aa hi jaati hai
Adayein shayaron jaisi
Unhe jab yaad karte hain
Tabhi barsaat aati hai
Deewaane hum nahin hote
Deewaani raat aati hai 
Hume unki uhne meri
Mohabbat yaad aati hai

Nahin koi gila humein
Jo na iss baar maanenge
Abhi chahe mana kar de
Kabhi toh yaar maanenge
Miley jo cheez aasani se 
Toh usme mazaa kaisa
Unhe mera banana tak
Na hum bhi haar maanenge
Suna hai chahatein sachi
Nahin barbaad jaati hain
Deewaane hum nahin hote
Deewaani raat aati hai 
Hume unki uhne meri
Mohabbat yaad aati hai

#akshaykumar #emraanhashmi #jacquelinefernandez

In this video, I ll be unboxing some amazing gifts that I have received for my new home. From decorative pieces to useful household items, there are so many thoughtful gifts that I cannot wait to share with you.

If you enjoy watching unboxing videos and want to see more, don't forget to hit that subscribe button and turn on notifications so you never miss out on our latest videos. We appreciate your support and look forward to sharing more exciting content with you.

Puranpoli | ‡§™‡•Å‡§∞‡§£‡§™‡•ã‡§≥‡•Ä ‚Äì 
‡§™‡•Å‡§∞‡§£ ‡§¨‡§®‡§µ‡§£‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ‡§∏‡§æ‡§†‡•Ä | For making Puran
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§π‡§∞‡§≠‡§∞‡§æ ‡§°‡§æ‡§≥ 2 ‡§µ‡§æ‡§ü‡•Ä | Bengal Gram 2 Cup
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§π‡§≥‡§¶ ¬º tsp | Turmeric ¬º tsp
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§§‡•á‡§≤ 2 ‡§ö‡§Æ‡§ö‡•á | Oil 2 tsp
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§™‡§æ‡§£‡•Ä | Water 
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§ó‡•Ç‡§≥ 2 ‡§µ‡§æ‡§ü‡•Ä | Jaggery 2 Cup
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§µ‡•á‡§≤‡§ö‡•Ä ‡§™‡•Ç‡§° ¬º tsp | Cardamom pw ¬º tsp
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§ú‡§æ‡§Ø‡§´‡§≥ ‡§™‡•Ç‡§° ¬º tsp | Nutmeg pw ¬º tsp
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§∏‡•Å‡§Ç‡§† ‡§™‡•Ç‡§° ‡•ß/‡•™ tsp | Ginger pw 1/4 tsp
‡§ï‡§£‡§ø‡§ï ‡§Æ‡§≥‡§£‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ‡§∏‡§æ‡§†‡•Ä | For making dough 
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§ó‡§µ‡•ç‡§π‡§æ‡§ö‡•á ‡§™‡•Ä‡§† 4 ‡§µ‡§æ‡§ü‡•Ä | Wheat flour 4 cups
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§Æ‡•Ä‡§† ¬Ω tsp | Salt to taste
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§§‡•á‡§≤ 2-3 ‡§ö‡§Æ‡§ö‡•á | oil 2-3 tsp
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§™‡§æ‡§£‡•Ä ‡§ó‡§∞‡§ú‡•á‡§®‡•Å‡§∏‡§æ‡§∞ | Water as required

Method ‚Äì
 ‚Ä¢ For making dough in a wheat flour add salt and knead the dough, rest for 20 mins and then apply some oil and knead soft dough again.
 ‚Ä¢ Wash and soak chana daal for about 30 minutes. 
 ‚Ä¢ Heat up water in a pressure cooker, add soaked daal along with water, add turmeric and oil and take 4-5 whistles on med heat.
 ‚Ä¢ Once cooked, separate daal and water. 
 ‚Ä¢ Once daal is at room temp, grind into mixer grinder.
 ‚Ä¢ Now add ground daal into a kadhai, add chopped jaggery and turn on the gas flame.
 ‚Ä¢ Now saute till mixture gets thickness then add cardamom and nutmeg powder.
 ‚Ä¢ Then turn off the heat and let the puran cool down completely. 
 ‚Ä¢ Now take ball size dough, dust some rice flour and fill the equal amount of puran and roll roti / puranpoli . dust rice flour whenever required,
 ‚Ä¢ Roast the puranpoli, apply ghee or oil.

snippet.title: Sunday Brunch With Venkatesh Daggubati & Rana Daggubati X Kamiya Jani | Ep 96 | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
We have two of the biggest South superstars on the show this time -  the uncle-nephew duo, Venkatesh Daggubati & Rana Daggubati. 

Now Mumbai cannot match up to Hyderabadi food so we treated them with what Mumbai is known for - Mumbaiya street food & chaat at Hitchki, BKC in Mumbai. Candidly, they spoke to us about their journeys, working in Bollywood & Telugu film industry, the food they like to eat, and a lot more. 

We played a fun game of, ‚ÄòHow Well Do You Know Each Other?‚Äô And surprisingly their answers were bang on. Watch to know more!  

Watch the entire episode and let us know in the comment section below which southern superstar should we call next on our show?

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3711 - 6 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3711: Holi Ki Taiyyari
--------------------------------------------------------
With Holi just around the corner, Tapu Sena surprises Sonu with some color. Despite Sonu's enthusiasm, Tapu Sena is told to save their elation for the celebration. His wife questions Sodhi about his "party sharty," but Bhide manages to spare him. Tapu Sena visits Bhide's home later. They paint everyone, but Bhide chastises them for painting the inside of the house; however, Madhavi let them because it is festival season. Tapu Sena has a novel way to celebrate Holi this year, which everyone is excited to know. What new concept does Tapu Sena have this time? Follow along!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3711, 6 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.
